### Helpers

#### [NEW] Helpers/PasswordHasher.cs
BCrypt hash/verify (จาก prototype — workFactor: 12)

---

### Repositories (6 คู่ Interface + Implementation)

| Interface | Implementation | หน้าที่ |
|-----------|---------------|---------|
| `IUserRepository` | `UserRepository` | CRUD Users, GetByUserName, UpdatePassword |
| `IRoleRepository` | `RoleRepository` | CRUD Roles, GetUserRoles |
| `IMenuRepository` | `MenuRepository` | CRUD Menus (tree structure) |
| `IRoleMenuPermissionRepository` | `RoleMenuPermissionRepository` | CRUD permissions per role×menu |
| `IRefreshTokenRepository` | `RefreshTokenRepository` | Create, GetByToken, Revoke, RevokeAll |
| `IPasswordResetRepository` | `PasswordResetRepository` | Create, GetByToken, MarkUsed, InvalidateAll |

ทุก repository ใช้ `IDbConnection` (Dapper) inject ผ่าน DI ตาม convention ของ imp-api

---

### Services (4 คู่)

| Interface | Implementation | หน้าที่ |
|-----------|---------------|---------|
| `IJwtService` | `JwtService` | Generate access token + refresh token |
| `IAuthService` | `AuthService` | Login, Register, Remember, ForgotPassword, ResetPassword, ChangePassword, Refresh, Logout |
| `IEmailService` | `EmailService` | Send password reset email (MailKit) |
| `IAdminService` | `AdminService` | Manage users/roles/menu permissions (Admin only) |

---

### DTOs

#### Auth DTOs (ใหม่)
- `LoginRequest` (UserName, Password, RememberMe)
- `RegisterRequest` (UserName, Password, DisplayName, Email)
- `ForgotPasswordRequest`, `ResetPasswordRequest`, `ChangePasswordRequest`
- `RefreshRequest`, `LogoutRequest`
- `AuthResponse` (AccessToken, RefreshToken, ExpiresIn, User, Menus+Permissions)
- `ErrorResponse`, `MessageResponse`

#### Admin DTOs (ใหม่)
- `CreateUserRequest`, `UpdateUserRequest`, `AssignRoleRequest`
- `CreateRoleRequest`, `UpdateRoleRequest`
- `SetMenuPermissionRequest`
- `MenuPermissionResponse`, `UserListResponse`, `RoleListResponse`

